snippet.title: Spider Fox Development Trailer
snippet.description:
An early look at Spider Fox mid development. Spider Fox is Available Now on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2478640/Spider_Fox/?utm_source=Youtube

A ridiculous, web slinging adventure game where you play as a Spider Fox. The Mad Scientist has made some wild animal combinations. Climb, use Grappling Webs, and other items to overcome his obstacles to save them all.
